extends ../ui_layout

block content

  .ui.text.container
    br
    h2 Standing Up Against Cyberbullying Pre-Activity Quiz
    form#cyber_pre.ui.reply.form(action='/prequiz/cyberbullying', method='POST')
      input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
      .ui.form
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='embarrassment_pre') You’ve always known that Tom isn’t well-liked at school but recently you've seen your classmates writing mean posts about him online, saying he’s “an embarrassment” and that it will be best if he leaves. What do you do?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='embarrassment_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Comment on a post saying "I know right? Nobody wants to see him.".
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='embarrassment_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Take a screenshot and post it with a comment saying "I agree!".
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='embarrassment_pre', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Comment on a post saying "You guys sound like jerks for saying that!".
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='friend_pre') Your best friend Cody tells you he has been very upset lately because his classmates are constantly making fun of him online, calling him things like “fat nerd” and “idiot”. You realize he’s being cyberbullied. What should you do?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friend_pre', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Help Cody tell an adult about the bullying.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friend_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Stop being friends with Cody because you don’t want to be bullied too.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friend_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Tell Cody to grow up and get over it.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='movement_pre') Recently your classmates started the “Ignore Sarah Movement”, because they dislike Sarah’s personality and they want to exclude her. Somebody sent you an invitation to this movement. What do you do?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='movement_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Reply “absolutely!” even though you don’t really know Sarah.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='movement_pre', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Tell Sarah about the invitation and make sure to include her next time someone ignores her.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='movement_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Share the invitation with more people. The more the merrier.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='behaviors_pre') Which of the following are things that a cyberbully might do?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='behaviors_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Making a fake profile to laugh at someone.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='behaviors_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Taking somebody’s picture and turning it into a hurtful meme.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='behaviors_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Leaving mean comments under someone’s dancing video.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='behaviors_pre', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label All of the above.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='actions_pre') Which of these are things you can do to stand up against cyberbullying?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='actions_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Reporting a mean post to the site it was posted on.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='actions_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Telling a trusted adult about something mean that you saw.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='actions_pre', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Telling people who are spreading rumors to stop.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='actions_pre', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label All of the above.
        h2 Just one more question... there are no right or wrong answers to this one!
        .grouped.fields
          label(for="use") Do you have an account on any social media sites?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='use', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Yes.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='use', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label No.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='use', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label I'm not sure.

        br
        button.ui.button(type='submit') Submit
    br
    br
    br
